title: Shorty Rogers - The Swinging Mr. Rogers (1955) PWR
description:
SHORTY ROGERS AND HIS JAZZ GIANTS - THE SWINGING MR. ROGERS (COMPLETE EDITION)

1. Isn't It Romantic?
2. Trickleydidlier
3. Oh! Play That Thing
4. Not Really The Blues
5. Martians Go Home
6. My Heart Stood Still
7. Michelle's Meditation
8. That's What I'm Talkin' Bout
9. Loaded
10. Bill
11. 12th Street Rag
12. The Lady In Red
13. Solarization

Shorty Rogers - trumpet
Jimmy Giuffre - clarinet, tenor & baritone sax
Pete Jolly - piano
Curtis Counce - bass
Shelly Manne - drums

Hollywood, March 1 (tracks 1, 3-6, 9-12)
& March 3 (tracks 2, 7-8 & 13), 1955

Bonus tracks (9-13) from the same seeions,
but not included on the original LP configuration.

2011 Poll Winners Records
